text: Antonio Alfaro (born 13 June 1956) is a Mexican equestrian. He competed in the individual eventing at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1956 births Category:Living people Category:Mexican male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Mexico Category:Equestrians at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
